.help gmosexamples March2012 gemini.gmos
.ih
NAME
gmosexamples - Print reduction examples to the screen
.ih
USAGE
gmosexamples example
.ih
PARAMETERS
.ls example (imaging|longslit|standard_longslit|MOS|NS_longslit|NS_MOS|IFU_1slit|IFU_2slit|standard_IFU)
Example script to print to the screen.
.le
.ih
DESCRIPTION

A few example scripts are provided for the GMOS package.
GMOSEXAMPLE prints these to the screen.
The examples use real data and have all been use for data reduction.
The users will need to modify directory and image names for their own use.
The example files are located in gmos$doc.

.nf
    Example              File
    ------------------------------------------------
    imaging              gmos_imaging_example.cl
    longslit             gmos_longslit_example.cl
    standard_longslit    gmos_longslit_standard_example.cl
    MOS                  gmos_mos_example.cl
    NS_longslit          gmos_ns_longslit_example.cl
    NS_MOS               gmos_ns_mos_example.cl
    IFU_1slit            gmos_ifu_1slit_example.cl
    IFU_2slit            gmos_ifu_2slit_example.cl
    standard_IFU         gmos_ifu_standard_example.cl
    ------------------------------------------------
.fi

To print the reduction example of imaging data, including fringe correction
if needed:

.nf
  cl> gmosexamples imaging
.fi

To print the reduction example of a longslit observation:

.nf
  cl> gmosexamples longslit
.fi

To print the reduction example of observation of spectrophotometric standard
star, including establishing the sensitivity function for (relative)
flux calibration:

.nf
  cl> gmosexamples standard_longslit
.fi

To print the reduction example of a MOS observation:

.nf
  cl> gmosexamples MOS
.fi

To print the reduction example of a Nod & Shuffle longslit observation

.nf
  cl> gmosexamples NS_longslit
.fi

To print the reduction example of a Nod & Shuffle MOS observation,
only the steps specific to N&S:

.nf
  cl> gmosexamples NS_MOS
.fi

To print the reduction example of an IFU observation taken in 1-slit mode:

.nf
  cl> gmosexamples IFU_1slit
.fi

To print the reduction example of an IFU observation taken in 2-slit mode:

.nf
  cl> gmosexamples IFU_2slit
.fi

To print the reduction example of an IFU observation of a spectrophotometric
standard star taken in 2-slit mode:

.nf
  cl> gmosexamples standard_IFU
.fi

.ih
BUGS AND LIMITATIONS
Improvements to the (previously semi-functional) variance and
data quality propagation in the GMOS package have undergone limited
testing; the accuracy of the results should still be verified at
each step by the scientist, particularly for spectroscopic data
reduction tasks.
.ih
